---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="The story behind CraftyDesi Woodworking and my commitment to handmade quality.">
	<section class="about-hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>The Maker Behind <span>the Wood</span></h1>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="about-content">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="about-grid">
				<div class="about-text">
					<h2>My Story</h2>
					<p>CraftyDesi Woodworking started as a way for me to reconnect with tangible craft in an increasingly digital world. As a working professional, I find balance in the slow, deliberate process of turning raw lumber into functional art.</p>
					
					<h2>My Process</h2>
					<p>Every project begins with the wood. I spend time selecting the right species and individual boards that will best suit the piece. My process is a mix of traditional hand-tool work and modern precision machinery.</p>
					
					<h2>Why Handmade?</h2>
					<p>In a world of mass-produced furniture, handmade items offer something different: soul. You can see the hand of the maker and the natural story of the tree in every piece I create.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="about-features">
					<div class="stat-card">
						<h3>Local Wood</h3>
						<p>Sourced from sustainable local mills.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-card">
						<h3>Custom Design</h3>
						<p>Built specifically for your space and needs.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-card">
						<h3>Built to Last</h3>
						<p>Furniture that will be passed down for generations.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<style>
		.about-hero {
			padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
			background: var(--color-surface);
			text-align: center;
			border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
		}
		.about-hero h1 {
			font-size: 3.5rem;
		}
		.about-hero h1 span {
			color: var(--color-primary);
		}

		.about-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
			gap: 5rem;
			padding-top: 4rem;
		}
		.about-text h2 {
			margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
		.about-text h2:first-child {
			margin-top: 0;
		}
		.about-text p {
			font-size: 1.125rem;
			color: var(--color-muted);
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}

		.about-features {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 2rem;
		}
		.stat-card {
			background: var(--color-surface);
			padding: 2rem;
			border-radius: 8px;
			border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
			box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
		}
		.stat-card h3 {
			margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			color: var(--color-primary-dark);
		}
		.stat-card p {
			color: var(--color-muted);
		}

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.about-grid {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			}
			.about-hero h1 {
				font-size: 2.5rem;
			}
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
